Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.25,0:01:21.39,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Fushigi na tabi ga hajimaru ze{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.25,0:01:21.39,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}¡Nuestro extraño viaje comienza!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:24.90,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Te ni irero! Doragon Booru{\i0}
